title:  "On Being a Female Founder & Startup CEO"
date:   2014-01-13
---

I've spent a great deal of time lately reflecting on my current career path. I'm the CEO of a small, boot-strapped technology startup. Nearly a year ago, I quit my desk job as an engineer in pursuit of a vision. Since then, I've come to identify with much more than just a mechanical engineer. 